descriptionHtml:
Description:

Beyond Skyrim presents a complete and legal recreation of the original Oblivion farmhouses.
This resource contains 7 new models, interiors and exteriors.

The thatch roof and the textures have been greatly enhanced from the original Oblivion versions. this file also contains a brand new windmill designed to match the rest of the set

For info on future releases and other updates about Beyond Skyrim, like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BeyondSkyrim
_______________________
Content:

The file contains the following resources:

Small Cyrodiil Farmhouse (interior and exterior)
Medium Cyrodiil Farmhouse (interior and exterior)
Large Cyrodiil Farmhousse/Inn (interior and exterior)
Cyrodiil Windmill (exterior only)



_______________________
Installation:

1: Place the meshes and textures folder in your skyrim data folder
2: Launch the creation kit
3: Right click on any static model in the object window and select new
4: Load the models from your data - Meshes - BSCyrodiil - Architecture - Farmhouse

Should you have any problems at all, be sure to contact me and I'll try to help you out as much as possible. the contact info found at the bottom of this page.
_______________________
Known Issues and bugs:

There are no LOD models in this package, LOD models will be created eventually, so be patient.
There is a minor bug on the fireplace in the Farmhouse03Interior model were some of the meshes are black, this will be fixed in a later version.
